"><div class=3D"ed4x0bn0 css-48o5u4 e1m4c3o81"><div class=3D"textBlock"><p>=
Assuming the height is <code>2 cm</code>, the segment area will be <code>11=
.18 cm=C2=B2</code>. You can calculate it using this formula:</p>
<p><code>r=C2=B2 =C3=97 arccos((r-h)/r) - (r-h) =C3=97 =E2=88=9A(2 =C3=97 r=
 =C3=97 h - h=C2=B2)</code></p></div></div></div><h3 data-testid=3D"What is=
